%N A397321 Expansion of e.g.f. (1/x) * Series_Reversion( x*(1 - x*(exp(x^4) - 1)) ).
%F A397321 E.g.f. A(x) satisfies A(x) = 1 + x * A(x)^2 * (exp((x * A(x))^4) - 1).
%F A397321 a(n) = (1/(n+1)) * Sum_{k=0..floor(n/4)} (2*n-4*k)! * Stirling2(k,n-4*k)/k!.
%o A397321 (PARI) a(n) = sum(k=0, n\4, (2*n-4*k)!*stirling(k, n-4*k, 2)/k!)/(n+1);
